10
00:01:09,640 --> 00:01:15,080
Introduced it to ninth leg of microchip UC3825N.

11
00:01:16,780 --> 00:01:37,040
Interesting property of this microchip is that at applying voltage rating 0.9 V starts current protection trigger, that is reduces duration of output pulses.

12
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:45,920
And this parameter from 0.9 V to 1.3 V lasts width reduction.

13
00:01:46,380 --> 00:01:57,320
At reaching amplitude voltage to 1.3 V at output fully stops generation of control pulses.

14
00:01:57,400 --> 00:02:00,600
That is such small window of possibilities.

15
00:02:01,140 --> 00:02:08,360
