And in mode when at you duration maximum, precisely when system triggers current protection, at this moment precisely will be heating of heat sink.

240
00:29:31,360 --> 00:29:33,040
But heating should be not strong.

241
00:29:34,300 --> 00:29:42,720
Approximately at... now will short system, look.

242
00:29:43,600 --> 00:29:45,840
Accumulator already drains of course.

243
00:29:49,760 --> 00:29:50,740
Look.

244
00:29:51,960 --> 00:29:57,440
There's heat release, order so 50 degrees.

245
00:29:58,600 --> 00:30:06,000
In such tough mode this converter not planned to operate, especially without blowing.

246
00:30:06,800 --> 00:30:09,080
So all normal.

247
00:30:09,900 --> 00:30:18,500
Next stage we need to tune so trigger of current protection.

248
00:30:18,660 --> 00:30:22,620
We now experiment conduct, picked this resistance here.

249
00:30:23,520 --> 00:30:34,920
To here add still variable resistance, we had smooth trigger regulation from 0.10 A to 20 A.

250
00:30:35,200 --> 00:30:37,260
Can set any regulation.

251
00:30:37,260 --> 00:30:44,680
Decided I to stop at such scheme solution of current protection regulation.

252
00:30:45,380 --> 00:30:50,380
It done on two resistances connected in series.

253
00:30:51,460 --> 00:30:56,600
And in parallel to one of them connected variable resistance.

254
00:30:57,400 --> 00:31:07,220
Thus, in case of exit of middle point of slider, we have current protection with help of these two resistances remains workable.

255
00:31:07,440 --> 00:31:19,340
And we don't risk getting into such situation when at wear, if we simply this point connected here, at some moment our system would remain without current protection.

256
00:31:19,400 --> 00:31:29,740
If this resistance remove, then system will work in mode of smallest current passing through power keys.

257
00:31:30,100 --> 00:31:32,960
Will supply smallest duration at their opening.

258
00:31:34,200 --> 00:31:35,920
Now show how this works.

259
00:31:36,660 --> 00:31:38,360
Approximately picked ratings.

260
00:31:38,640 --> 00:31:40,320
Further slightly will change.

261
00:31:41,120 --> 00:31:41,940
Announce.

262
00:31:41,980 --> 00:31:47,240
0.7 Ohm, 120 Ohm and 1 kOhm this resistance.

263
00:31:48,100 --> 00:31:49,300
Apply power.

264
00:31:52,200 --> 00:32:01,580
Regulation starts from 1 Amp and to 19 Amps.

265
00:32:02,220 --> 00:32:03,900
Add with slider.

266
00:32:08,460 --> 00:32:10,520
Slowly move.

267
00:32:11,400 --> 00:32:15,500
See, current protection how works now.

268
00:32:16,880 --> 00:32:24,300
Tune for example 2 Amps consumption.

269
00:32:25,000 --> 00:32:29,740
Further 5 Amps consumption.

270
00:32:30,320 --> 00:32:34,340
See duration of control pulses.

271
00:32:38,910 --> 00:32:47,310
And already not important how we control output voltage, can only its reduce.

272
00:32:47,590 --> 00:32:54,750
But at increase to maximum, we and will have our desired tuned with this slider.

273
00:32:55,650 --> 00:32:59,790
Seems resistance slightly got low-quality.

274
00:32:59,950 --> 00:33:01,610
There sharp jerks.

275
00:33:02,130 --> 00:33:03,310
Will need replace.

276
00:33:03,990 --> 00:33:05,310
But this all fixable.

277
00:33:05,530 --> 00:33:06,910
Now bring to maximum.

278
00:33:08,330 --> 00:33:09,830
18 Amps.

279
00:33:11,470 --> 00:33:15,410
Yes, resistance need change, but regulation present.

280
00:33:18,730 --> 00:33:21,870
So at such scheme can stop.

281
00:33:24,930 --> 00:33:32,110
On this can consider tuning of current protection finished.

